title: MSG CX Series Races5&6:Presented By,Town Of Unicoi
Tornado Cross
description: Tornado Cross:  2nd CX race on the beautiful King College campus.  In support of the King College Cycling Team.
course: On King College Campus through wooded section and around lake.  Fast course with some steep climbs.
registration: Registration will begin at 10:00am.  You may register until 15 minutes before the start of each race.  All racers must present a valid racing license.  Unlicensed riders wil be required to purchase a $10.00 \'one day license\' and be placed in CX 4 men or women.
